  "body_text": "View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/bf258eda-a3cc-483a-a2cd-a8f0ab8971e6/evolving-ai-logo.png?t=1775813177)\r\nFollow image link: (http://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\nCaption: \r\n\r\n[Subscribe](http://evolvingai.io/subscribe) | [Advertise](https://app.beehiiv.com/direct_sponsorships/b0b3eadc-1525-42f7-a9bd-8ac2680c49db)\r\n\r\n----------\r\nView image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/835016e0-7dbb-44fc-aa51-43f92dfcace2/newsletter-header-new.jpg?t=1756031901)\r\nCaption: \r\n\r\n## Welcome, AI enthusiasts\r\n\r\nFor the last 3 years, we’ve built the largest AI community in the world, now followed by over 5,000,000 dedicated AI enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nBut keeping up with AI is one thing. Knowing how to actually use it in your work is another.\r\n\r\nThat’s exactly what we’re going to solve. We’re launching our first quarterly workshop, where we break down the most important developments from Q1 and turn them into practical workflows you can apply right away.\r\n\r\nAs a newsletter reader, you’ll get access to a _discounted spot_ at the end. **Let’s dive in!**\r\n\r\n———————————————————————————\r\n\r\n**What you’ll get by joining:**\r\n\r\n* **6 hours, live and interactive, not a lecture, but a build session**\r\n\r\n* **Covers every major model, tool, and workflow shift from Q1**\r\n\r\n* **No coding required**\r\n\r\n* **The Q1 AI Brief Toolkit included with every registration**\r\n\r\n* **Access to the private community**\r\n\r\nLearn more (https://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\n\r\n\r\n----------\r\n\r\n----------\r\n## **THE AI BRIEF**\r\n⚡️ [**Introducing AI Brief - Evolving AI's Quarterly Workshop**](https://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\n\r\nView image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/9a3a1c37-e33d-4a92-a4cd-36390b9ff687/ai_brief.jpeg?t=1775984348)\r\nFollow image link: (https://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\nCaption: \r\n\r\n[Turn AI into something you actually use in your work every day →](https://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\n\r\nThis is the first time we are doing a workshop, and we didn’t build it to be another webinar you half-watch from a second tab.\r\n\r\nAI Brief is a live, 6-hour quarterly workshop where we take everything that moved in AI this quarter and turn it into real workflows and use cases.\r\n\r\nThis is not slides or summaries. It is a build session where you leave with something that works.\r\n\r\nWe’ve spent years giving 5 million+ people the signal on AI. AI Brief is where that signal becomes skill.\r\n\r\n**Here's what's inside:**\r\n\r\n* Every major model, tool, and shift from Q1 2026, curated, explained, and made useful\r\n\r\n* Role-specific updates curated for PMs, founders, engineers, marketers, and designers\r\n\r\n* A hands-on build session where you walk away with at least 3 workflows ready to use the next day\r\n\r\n* The Q1 AI Brief Toolkit, including a prompt library and workflow templates that you keep\r\n\r\n* If you can’t join live, the full recording is delivered within 24 hours with access for the next 90 days\r\n\r\n* Downloadable decks and slides\r\n\r\n* Access to a private community to ask questions, network, and grow\r\n\r\nGet inside → (https://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\n\r\n**Who's this for?**\r\n\r\nIf you follow Evolving AI, you are exactly at the right level. No coding required and no prior courses needed. This is for professionals who are AI-aware but do not know what really matters and want to move from confusion to actually using it. \r\n\r\nThe gap between those two things is exactly what AI Brief was built to close.\r\n\r\n**One last thing**\r\n\r\nGet $50 off with code \r\n**EARLYBIRD-NEWSLETTER** at checkout.\r\n\r\nMost workshops throw discount codes everywhere. Not us, we created exactly one true exclusive coupon code for AI Brief, and it's sitting in this email for our newsletter subscribers.\r\n\r\nNo other platform, no other audience. Just you.\r\nThis is the lowest AI Brief will ever be priced.\r\n\r\n[**Be in the room. April 19th → **](http://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)[Start Q2 ahead](http://aibrief.evolvingai.io/)\r\n\r\n\r\n----------\r\n\r\n----------\r\n\r\n----------\r\n———\r\n\r\nYou are reading a plain text version of this post. For the best experience, copy and paste this link in your browser to view the post online:\r\nhttps://evolvingai.io/p/this-fixes-your-ai-confusion\r\n",
